name: Wall Street Journal Subscription
short_description: The Wall Street Journal print franchise has more than 750 journalists world-wide, part of the Dow Jones network of nearly 1,800 business and financial news staff in bureaus across the globe. Other publications that are part of The Wall Street Journal franchise, with a total circulation of 2.7 million, include The Wall Street Journal Asia; The Wall Street Journal Europe; and The Wall Street Journal Online http://zencleanse.org/wall-street-journal-subscription-wsj-subscription-discount-80.html
